---
import { party } from '../data/site';
---
<section class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-10 px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.92fr] lg:px-8 lg:py-28">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-4 top-10 hidden h-28 w-px bg-cyan-200/35 lg:block"></div>
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Transmission from 2040 · Alliance public relay</p>
    <h1 class="text-balance mt-5 max-w-5xl text-6xl font-black tracking-[-0.08em] text-cyan-50 sm:text-8xl lg:text-9xl">
      <span class="block bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 via-cyan-100 to-violet-100 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-[0_0_28px_rgba(143,232,226,0.18)]">Futurekind</span>
      <span class="block text-[0.62em] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100/72">Alliance</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight text-lime-100 sm:text-3xl">{party.slogan}</p>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-cyan-50/70">{party.shortLine}</p>
    <div class="mt-8 max-w-xl rounded-[1.4rem] border border-cyan-200/18 bg-black/24 p-3 shadow-[0_0_34px_rgba(143,232,226,0.10)]">
      <img src="/assets/alliance-wordmark-2040-02.svg" alt="Futurekind Alliance wordmark" class="w-full rounded-[1rem]" loading="eager" />
    </div>
    <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a class="focus-ring rounded-full border border-cyan-200/50 bg-cyan-200 px-6 py-3 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#030711] shadow-[0_0_34px_rgba(143,232,226,0.26)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-cyan-100" href="/manifesto/">Open manifesto</a>
      <a class="focus-ring rounded-full border border-violet-200/35 bg-violet-200/10 px-6 py-3 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-50 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-violet-200/18" href="/federation/">View federation map</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid max-w-2xl gap-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan-100/54 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <span class="border-l border-cyan-200/35 pl-3">Public-interest AI</span>
      <span class="border-l border-cyan-200/35 pl-3">Exit rights encoded</span>
      <span class="border-l border-cyan-200/35 pl-3">Commons infrastructure</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dark-panel relative min-h-[34rem] overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-10 top-12 h-px scanline"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 size-64 rounded-full bg-cyan-300/12 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 left-2 size-72 rounded-full bg-violet-400/12 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="relative rounded-[1.5rem] border border-cyan-200/20 bg-black/22 p-5">
      <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100/58">
        <span>FK-A / civicnet node</span>
        <span>2040.11.03</span>
      </div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-[1.4rem] border border-cyan-200/24 bg-cyan-200/[0.03] shadow-[inset_0_0_60px_rgba(143,232,226,0.07)]">
        <img src="/assets/civicnet-map-2040-02.svg" alt="Civicnet federation relay map for Futurekind Alliance member chapters" class="w-full" loading="eager" />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-sm text-cyan-50/72 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <span class="rounded-2xl border border-cyan-200/18 bg-cyan-200/7 p-4">AI advises. People decide.</span>
        <span class="rounded-2xl border border-cyan-200/18 bg-cyan-200/7 p-4">Federated colonies, not empires.</span>
        <span class="rounded-2xl border border-cyan-200/18 bg-cyan-200/7 p-4">Exit, fork, rejoin with dignity.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
